197
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,780
Benar.

198
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:17,680
Oh! Itu Petugas Takagi!

199
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:19,880
Dor!

200
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:28,180
Hei, ada apa? Takagi!

201
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:34,859
Oh, itu Petugas Takagi!

202
00:10:35,659 --> 00:10:36,759
Dor!

203
00:10:40,859 --> 00:10:43,659
Hei, apa-apaan ini?

204
00:10:43,659 --> 00:10:45,859
Tapi apa yang kami lihat...

205
00:10:45,859 --> 00:10:47,859
Sama seperti itu juga!

206
00:10:47,859 --> 00:10:50,559
Jadi, dua orang memainkan satu orang!

207
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:52,659
Takagi dan bocah detektif dari Osaka itu

208
00:10:52,659 --> 00:10:54,659
mencoba memerankannya!

209
00:10:54,959 --> 00:10:57,659
Ini benar-benar telihat alami jika kau melakukannya dengan benar.

210
00:10:57,659 --> 00:10:58,859
Takagi itu...

211
00:11:00,459 --> 00:11:03,359
Lekas turun dan jelaskan, Takagi!

212
00:11:03,359 --> 00:11:04,659
Ya, tuan.

213
00:11:07,059 --> 00:11:08,459
Petugas Takagi?

214
00:11:08,459 --> 00:11:09,959
Oh, begini...

215
00:11:11,259 --> 00:11:13,859
Takagi! Tentang apa itu tadi?

216
00:11:13,859 --> 00:11:16,759
Aku... aku hanya disuruh untuk tetap di sini

217
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:21,159
